  - HSI subsystem;
  - Ethernet team driver;
  - Ext4 file system;
  - Timer subsystem;
  - DCCP (Datagram Congestion Control Protocol);
  - IPv6 networking;
  - NET/ROM layer;
  - SCTP protocol;
  - USB sound devices;
